{"tha-ap34:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap34:0.2":"Kundadhanavagga ","tha-ap34:0.3":"Sagatattheraapadana ","tha-ap34:1.1":"“Sobhito nama namena, ","tha-ap34:1.2":"ahosim brahmano tada; ","tha-ap34:1.3":"Purakkhato sasissehi, ","tha-ap34:1.4":"aramam agamasaham. ","tha-ap34:2.1":"Bhagava tamhi samaye, ","tha-ap34:2.2":"bhikkhusanghapurakkhato; ","tha-ap34:2.3":"Aramadvara nikkhamma, ","tha-ap34:2.4":"atthasi purisuttamo. ","tha-ap34:3.1":"Tamaddasasim sambuddham, ","tha-ap34:3.2":"dantam dantapurakkhatam; ","tha-ap34:3.3":"Sakam cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap34:3.4":"santhavim lokanayakam. ","tha-ap34:4.1":"Ye keci padapa sabbe, ","tha-ap34:4.2":"mahiya te viruhare; ","tha-ap34:4.3":"Buddhimanto tatha satta, ","tha-ap34:4.4":"ruhanti jinasasane. ","tha-ap34:5.1":"Satthavahosi sappanno, ","tha-ap34:5.2":"mahesi bahuke jane; ","tha-ap34:5.3":"Vipatha uddharitvana, ","tha-ap34:5.4":"patham acikkhase tuvam. ","tha-ap34:6.1":"Danto dantaparikinno, ","tha-ap34:6.2":"jhayi jhanaratehi ca; ","tha-ap34:6.3":"Atapi pahitattehi, ","tha-ap34:6.4":"upasantehi tadibhi. ","tha-ap34:7.1":"Alankato parisahi, ","tha-ap34:7.2":"punnananehi sobhati; ","tha-ap34:7.3":"Pabha niddhavate tuyham, ","tha-ap34:7.4":"suriyodayane yatha. ","tha-ap34:8.1":"Pasannacittam disvana, ","tha-ap34:8.2":"mahesi padumuttaro; ","tha-ap34:8.3":"Bhikkhusanghe thito sattha, ","tha-ap34:8.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap34:9.1":"‘Yo so hasam janetvana, ","tha-ap34:9.2":"mamam kittesi brahmano; ","tha-ap34:9.3":"Kappanam satasahassam, ","tha-ap34:9.4":"devaloke ramissati. ","tha-ap34:10.1":"Tusita hi cavitvana, ","tha-ap34:10.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap34:10.3":"Gotamassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap34:10.4":"sasane pabbajissati. ","tha-ap34:11.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap34:11.2":"arahattam labhissati; ","tha-ap34:11.3":"Sagato nama namena, ","tha-ap34:11.4":"hessati satthu savako’. ","tha-ap34:12.1":"Pabbajitvana kayena, ","tha-ap34:12.2":"papakammam vivajjayim; ","tha-ap34:12.3":"Vaciduccaritam hitva, ","tha-ap34:12.4":"ajivam parisodhayim. ","tha-ap34:13.1":"Evam viharamanoham, ","tha-ap34:13.2":"tejodhatusu kovido; ","tha-ap34:13.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap34:13.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap34:14.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap34:14.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap34:14.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap34:15.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sagato thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap34:16.1":"Sagatattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}